item.title: What does it mean when cauliflower is fuzzy?

Optimally, the cauliflower head is harvested before that condition occurs. Can you eat cauliflower that is fuzzy? The cauliflower is not adversely affected, except by the appearance. The defect has no bearing on the taste of the cauliflower.
